info.author: Ilkka Tuohela
info.description:
This module contains some parser classes and utility scripts for network
security scan report file processing and review.

Supported formats are:

- NMAP xml reports
- Nessus xml reports (v2)
- MBSA xml reports

... and others. 

The example scripts are in the bin directory and are installed automatically.

This module is under quite heavy development and changes. Please report any 
regressions or new bugs to hile@iki.fi, I'll try to stabilize the code base 
in 2.x series, first release was just a quick'n'dirty version.
